    {
      "id": "1521910349606158556",
      "type": "Reply",
      "timestamp": "2026-07-01T16:08:23.073+00:00",
      "timestampEdited": null,
      "callEndedTimestamp": null,
      "isPinned": false,
      "content": "I think what you will find is that some bit will always be the same at power-on but some will likely be more random. This means you'll need to transform this power-up pattern with random bits into a reproducible one.",
